{"word":"G3905 - παρατείνω - parateínō - par-at-i'-no - Continue","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρατείνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parateínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-at-i'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Continue</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொடர்"},{"paragraph":"to extend beside, to stretch out lengthwise, to extend; to prolong"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>teino&#x0304;</b> (to <i>stretch</i>); to <i>extend along</i>, that is, <i>prolong</i> (in point of time): - continue.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}